  "body": "**üìù Details**\r\n\r\nFor ERC20Wrapper, the Upgradeable version's [`underlying` variable is public ](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts-upgradeable/blob/master/contracts/token/ERC20/extensions/ERC20WrapperUpgradeable.sol#L22) and the immutable is removed.\r\n\r\nWe don't want that since child contracts should not be able to override it.\r\n\r\nIt's then needed to replace the `public` visibility of the `underlying` variable [in the ERC20Wrapper contract](https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/a035b235b4f2c9af4ba88edc4447f02e37f8d124/contracts/token/ERC20/extensions/ERC20Wrapper.sol#L19) and create a public view function that replaces its access.",
